==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: fishing expedition
<hw>fishing expedition</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>An investigation
searching for evidence of wrongdoing, with no credible evidence of such
wrongdoing available at the outset of the investigation, and often
without specifying in advance the wrongdoing to be proven.</def>
<mark>[metaphorical]</mark> ⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

